getType

java.lang.String getType()
Get the type of the depenendency. Possible values are AGENTTYPE_DEPENDENCY, AGENTINSTANCE_DEPENDENCY, SOCIETYTYPE_DEPENDENCY, SOCIETYINSTANCE_DEPENDENCY, SERVICE_DEPENDENCY, DELAY_DEPENDENCY.

Returns:
The type of the dependency.

isActive

boolean isActive()
Return whether this is an active dependency or not. The ASCML activly engages in fulfilling an active dependency or just waits for a not-active dependency to hold.

Returns:
true, if this is an active dependency, false otherwise.

setActive

void setActive(boolean active)
Set whether this is an active dependency or not. The ASCML activly engages in fulfilling an active dependency or just waits for a not-active dependency to hold.

Parameters:
active - true, if this is an active dependency, false otherwise.
